    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, currently maintained in showroom condition. This specimen represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that aligns with its aesthetic perfection. This is, without compromise, an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand the pinnacle of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
